We got a few things to do.

1285
01:19:37,840 --> 01:19:40,286
- It's all about you.
- Mmm-hmm.

1286
01:19:40,520 --> 01:19:42,921
I already had my career. I did okay.

1287
01:19:43,080 --> 01:19:45,401
