not really my crowd, you know?

1350
01:23:47,880 --> 01:23:48,881
Yeah, I can see.

1351
01:23:49,080 --> 01:23:50,730
Look, it's the boxing boy,
Lil Apollo Creed.

1352
01:23:50,960 --> 01:23:52,530
