don't get the treatment.

1466
01:32:02,760 --> 01:32:05,127
So if I fight, you fight.

1467
01:32:37,800 --> 01:32:39,529
- Hey.
- What's up?

1468
01:32:39,680 --> 01:32:41,091
You been to the gym?

1469
01:32:41,520 --> 01:32:42,726
Nah, I've been here.

1470
01:32:42,880 --> 01:32:45,724
